videos.description: Trojan's Ronald Jones II breaks a tackle for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jones breaks tackle for USC's second TD

videos.description: After a missed Oregon State field goal, Sam Darnold gives the ball right back after the ball slips out of his hands on a pass attempt.
videos.headline: Darnold loses the ball mid-throw

videos.description: Sam Darnold finds Deontay Burnett in the end zone for Darnold's second touchdown pass of the game.
videos.headline: Darnold lobs it to the end zone for TD

videos.description: Sam Darnold finds Steven Mitchell Jr. for 19 yards and Mitchell breaks the tackle with a nice spin move.
videos.headline: USC's Mitchell breaks tackle with spin move

videos.description: Oregon State's Manase Hungalu picks off Sam Darnold in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Darnold is picked off by Beavers' Hungalu

videos.description: Sam Darnold pass is complete to Josh Falo for a 30-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: USC's Falo gets first career TD

videos.description: Oregon State's Darell Garretson finds Seth Collins who makes a great one-handed catch for 33 yards.
videos.headline: Beavers' Collins makes great one-handed catch

videos.description: Oregon State Darell Garretson fumbles the ball on 2nd and goal, which leads leads to USC recovering  ball.
videos.headline: Beavers' fumble snap in scoring position

videos.description: Sam Darnold gets sacked for a loss of 21 yards and is recovered by USC's Toa Lobendahn and returned for 0 yards.
videos.headline: Darnold gets sacked for a loss of 21 yards

videos.description: Seth Collins looks like he makes a great touchdown catch, but is marked down six inches short after a review. To make things worse, Collins picks up an unsportsmanlike penalty for taunting after the catch.
videos.headline: Beavers fail twice on apparent TD

videos.description: Beavers Artavis Pierces' runs up the middle for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Pierce plows ahead for TD

videos.description: Trojans' Sam Darnold scrambles and finds Aca'Cedric Ware for a 37-yard completion.
videos.headline: Darnold scrambles for 37-yard completion

videos.description: Oregon State's Darell Garretson throws deep to Xavier Hawkins for a 38-yard pass for a Beavers 1st down.
videos.headline: Beavers' Garretson throws deep to get into USC territory

videos.description: In USC's blowout win, blind snapper Jake Olson enters the game to snap the ball for the extra point.
videos.headline: Another special moment for USC's Olson

videos.description: Sam Darnold throws for 316 yards, three touchdowns and an interception as No. 14 USC defeats Oregon State 38-10.
videos.headline: USC bounces back in rout of Oregon State
